t\":\"fixed\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-image uagb-block-2aae2944-a7ac-4765-9200-5c94b3fcf50c\"><div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\"></div><div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size has-very-light-gray-background-color\"> What is WordPress? At its core,&nbsp;<strong>WordPress is the simplest, most popular way to create your own website or blog.&nbsp;</strong>In fact, WordPress powers&nbsp;over 35.2%&nbsp;of all the websites on the Internet. Yes – more than one in four websites that you visit are likely powered by WordPress. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size has-very-light-gray-background-color\"> On a slightly more technical level, WordPress is an open-source content management system licensed under GPLv2, which means that anyone can use or modify the WordPress software for free. A content management system is basically a tool that makes it easy to manage important aspects of your website – like content – without needing to know anything about programming.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size has-very-light-gray-background-color\">   The end result is that WordPress makes building a website accessible to anyone – even people who aren’t developers.    </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></section>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/section -->\n\n<!-- wp:uagb/section {\"classMigrate\":true,\"block_id\":\"9ebffe1d-59d8-4d04-bc80-1363716e16bb\"} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined uagb-block-9ebffe1d-59d8-4d04-bc80-1363716e16bb\"><div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\"></div><div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\"><!-- wp:core-embed/youtube /--></div></section>\n<!-- /wp:uagb/section -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'What Is WordPress? Explained for Beginners.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2020-01-21 17:52:09', '2020-01-21 17:52:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/quiz/?page_id=65', -1, 'page', '', 0),
